
<%- include("../../views/partials/user/headers") %>

  <style>
    .nav-menu #about {
      color: #00c3ff;
    }

    .nav-menu #about {
      font-size: 19px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .about-container {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .hero-section {
      background-color: #1a1a2e;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 60px 0;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .hero-section h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #00FFFB;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .pcontainer {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .about-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .about-text {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 300px;
    }

    .about-image {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 300px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .featured-image {
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h2 {
      color: #1a1a2e;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin: 30px 0 20px;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    ul {
      margin-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .values-section {
      margin: 40px 0 60px;
    }

    .values-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .value-card {
      box-shadow: rgba(50, 50, 93, 0.25) 0px 50px 100px -20px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 0px 30px 60px -30px, rgba(10, 37, 64, 0.35) 0px -2px 6px 0px inset;
      background: #FFFF;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 1) 0%, rgba(187, 253, 252, 0.72) 100%);
      padding: 30px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    }

    .value-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgb(0, 0, 0);
    }

    .value-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #1a1a2e;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .value-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #00FFFB;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-section {
        padding: 40px 0;
      }

      .hero-section h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .about-grid {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .values-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .values-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
  <main class="about-container">
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>About Voxera</h1>
        <p class="tagline">Premium Audio Solutions for Every Lifestyle</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-content">
      <div class="pcontainer">
        <div class="about-grid">
          <div class="about-text">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Founded with a passion for exceptional sound quality, Voxera began with a simple mission: to create
              audio products that elevate your listening experience without breaking the bank.</p>
            <p>Since our inception, we've been dedicated to crafting headsets, earbuds, neckbands, and wired solutions
              that combine cutting-edge technology with comfortable design. We believe that premium audio experiences
              should be accessible to everyone.</p>

            <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
            <p>At Voxera, we're committed to:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Quality Sound:</strong> Delivering rich, immersive audio experiences across all our products
              </li>
              <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> Constantly evolving our technology to stay ahead of industry trends</li>
              <li><strong>Durability:</strong> Creating products that withstand daily use and stand the test of time
              </li>
              <li><strong>Customer Satisfaction:</strong> Ensuring that every customer finds the perfect audio solution
                for their needs</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="about-image">
            <img src="/img/voxera.png" alt="Voxera Headphones Collection" class="featured-image">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="values-section">
          <h2>Why Choose voxera?</h2>
          <div class="values-grid">
            <div class="value-card">
              <div class="value-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-headphones"></i>
              </div>
              <h3>Sound Expertise</h3>
              <p>Our team of audio engineers fine-tune each product for exceptional clarity and depth.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value-card">
              <div class="value-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-medal"></i>
              </div>
              <h3>Premium Quality</h3>
              <p>We use high-grade materials and rigorous testing to ensure product excellence.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value-card">
              <div class="value-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
              </div>
              <h3>Customer First</h3>
              <p>Your satisfaction drives our innovation and product development process.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value-card">
              <div class="value-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
              </div>
              <h3>Global Standards</h3>
              <p>We adhere to international quality standards for all our audio solutions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include("../../views/partials/user/footers") %>